<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3097] LocalRepository is not updated when bundles are</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3097</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The local repository should contain resources for currently installed bundles but these can be out of date if a bundle is updated because the listener only responds to INSTALLED and UNINSTALLED bundle events.  It should also handle UPDATED events.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
